---

---

<section id="about" class="w-full bg-linear-to-br from-slate-500 to-slate-600 p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 rounded-t-[110px] md:rounded-t-[200px] rounded-b-[110px] md:rounded-b-[200px] shadow-all">

    <div class="flex font-semibold flex-col mx-auto max-w-7xl mb-12 md:mb-14 items-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl text-amber-700 px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-200/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg shadow-lg translate-y-3">About MixxFit</h3>
    </div>

   <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_1fr] gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden min-h-85 sm:min-h-105 lg:min-h-140 flex items-center justify-center p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-14">

            <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg aspect-square rounded-[34%] bg-linear-to-b from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600 p-10 sm:p-12 lg:p-14 flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-yellow-300/30 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-white transition duration-200">
            <img src="/logo-2.png" alt="MixxFit logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)]">
         </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-slate-50 flex flex-col gap-5 md:gap-6">

         <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight font-semibold text-center">
            A fitness tracker that
            <span class="text-amber-300">respects your time</span>
         </h2>

         <p class="text-lg text-slate-100/85 leading-relaxed text-center">
            MixxFit started as a personal workout logging tool and evolved into a focused tool for people who want to train hard, track body weight, and stay consistent without app clutter.
            No noise, no gimmicks, just your routine and clear progress.
         </p>

         <div class="mt-2 flex flex-col gap-5 p-6 pb-20 sm:pb-0">
            <article class="flex items-start gap-6">
               <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-yellow-500 text-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
               </div>
               <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl/none md:text-[1.65rem] font-semibold">Built for consistency</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-slate-100/80 text-lg">Every screen is designed to remove friction, because progress only happens when tracking becomes a habit.</p>
               </div>
            </article>

            <article class="flex items-start gap-6">
               <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-yellow-500 text-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-simple text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
               </div>
               <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl/none md:text-[1.65rem] font-semibold">Data that keeps you honest</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-slate-100/80 text-lg">Simple charts for training volume and weight trends help you see momentum week by week.</p>
               </div>
            </article>

            <article class="flex items-start gap-6">
               <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-yellow-500 text-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-code text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
               </div>
               <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl/none md:text-[1.65rem] font-semibold">Crafted by a solo developer</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-slate-100/80 text-lg">MixxFit is designed and shipped by one developer who trains, tracks, and improves the product through real daily use.</p>
               </div>
            </article>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div>
</section>
